{"type": "article", "id": 18974, "title": "朋友圈里的精彩人生，不这么装一装怎么过？丨好奇心研究所", "description": "多谢贡献答案的各位好奇心读者～", "date": "2015-12-13T08:00:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6475, "name": "朋友圈"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 234, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135702rSZetAy6ql9UgzKH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t1. 一个人无聊的旅行，假装自由又开心。@ MissQ-Peachy\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135648fLokwGYgva17XRye.gif\" width=\"245\" height=\"180\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.73469388\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t2. 出国旅游一次, 照片发半年。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135649lnZ4TgDoe2kdmMBN.gif\" width=\"450\" height=\"250\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55555556\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t3. 自我感觉非常段子手。然而并没有一个赞。<span>@</span>三茄子\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135650LEhFbc5jX6xRPmY2.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t4. 深夜发吃，其实并不好吃。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021356514j8MthzkxVvEN2d0.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t5. 不会喝酒，硬要发酒照。<span>@ claps down</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021356526mY90enENFfKIhpJ.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"200\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t6. 黑咖啡，其实觉得很苦。<span>@ CPC</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021356539ehKJ3dH0WBEVAiF.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t7. 其实吉他钢琴什么的<span>弹</span>得不怎么样，但是天天提起。<span>@</span>默片时代\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135653oJAT9BE8bNqdIsRD.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>8. 很多书的书架，其实一本没读。 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135654EYBaop5usWAdzPD1.gif\" width=\"360\" height=\"188\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.52222222\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t9. 偶尔搞一下学习，搞得好像自己是个勤奋又上进的青年一样。<span>@</span>草克力\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135655BQcJIu5vw6nPMyCT.gif\" title=\"我\" alt=\"我\" data-ratio=\"0.67483296\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t10. 快乐的时候分享出来哪怕是一件很小的事。我把自己的悲伤痛苦隐藏起来绝对不发出去哪怕是很严重的事。@Un\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135658gZz9dEkaG0iMHxYP.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t11. 把猫拍得很美，假装闻不到 shi 味。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135659qd3jf4A0KClUsJ8x.gif\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t12. 假装高冷从不发朋友圈。其实知道没人关心。<span>@</span>魏合\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135700zve2Zm7pIsd6JYMP.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t13. 假装很忙不发朋友圈。其实特别闲。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145706qLHiRcUZmov80K7Y.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t14. 温暖美好的合照，其实私下刚吵架。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135700TMf2WA8175KIeRcH.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t15. 化一个小时妆只为自拍。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135701w3Ursek4869ASIQO.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t16. 看到大家都是假装的，我就安心了。@橘小麦\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135701DYbVlMtULeJkfmGB.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<em>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}